reviews.text: The service was awful, the food was mediocore, and I personally wonder how well trained the staff are with food cleanliness and hygiene. The tables and the floor was greasy, the waitress seemed to was wearing plastic gloves, but she kept taking them off and shoving them into her backpocket and reusing it... She dropped a receipt in my noodle soup and just fished it out with her hands.
Not a big eatery at causeway bay branch. Porridge and fried XO carrot cake dough stick quite tasty. Usually if I stay at parklane l will definitely go there for breakfast.
I was having stomach discomfort and the congee is such a great option for me. Smooth and nice.

They provide good foods and good service.
👍
Not bad

reviews.text: 環境舒適、食品多源化。
新式粥店，售賣的食物花款多。
難食，得過且過!無留戀

今日黎食粥，原來好多款的食物菜式選擇，好耐無黎過食！
點了雙拼粥配半份油條，更加錢配炒麵，抵食又飽肚！
雙丸粥（熱辣辣香噴噴，鮮豬肉丸爽口彈牙；蝦米鯪魚球香滑軟熟，各有3粒；粥綿又滑）油條脆口、炒麵唔油又大份又軟硬剛好！

お店は狭くてキレイではないけど、お粥は安めで美味しいです。
下手に高級粥のお店に行かなくてもここで十分美味しいです。
